.TH TP-LINT 1 "February 2026" "tp-lint 1.8.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
tp-lint \- Translation Project linter and statistics tool
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B tp-lint
[\fIOPTIONS\fR] [\fILANG\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B tp-lint
downloads and lints PO files from the GNU Translation Project.
Shows coverage statistics and generates reports for translation teams.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-h ", " \-\-help
Show help message and exit.
.TP
.BR \-v ", " \-\-version
Show version number and exit.
.TP
.BR \-l ", " \-\-list
List all available languages.
.TP
.BR \-s ", " \-\-stats " " [\fILANG\fR]
Show translation statistics.
.TP
.BR \-d ", " \-\-domain " " \fIPKG\fR
Filter to specific package/domain.
.TP
.BR \-\-no\-lint
Download only, don't run l10n-lint.
.TP
.BR \-p ", " \-\-package " " \fIPKG\fR
Only lint specific package(s). Can be repeated.
.TP
.BR \-r ", " \-\-report " " [\fILANG\fR]
Generate translation status report.
.TP
.BR \-\-report\-format " " \fIFORMAT\fR
Report format: markdown (default), html
.TP
.BR \-V ", " \-\-verbose
Show detailed progress.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
List all available languages:
.B tp-lint -l
.TP
Lint all Swedish PO files:
.B tp-lint sv
.TP
Lint only coreutils for Swedish:
.B tp-lint -d coreutils sv
.TP
Download only (no linting):
.B tp-lint --no-lint sv
.TP
Generate HTML report:
.B tp-lint -r sv --report-format html --report-output sv.html
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Success.
.TP
.B 1
Error occurred or lint issues found.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR l10n-lint (1),
.BR po-translate (1)
